# CODEOWNERS - Defines code review ownership for governed IaC repository
#
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone opens a pull request.
# Documentation: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default owner for everything in the repo
*       @hummbl-dev

# Infrastructure code requires security-focused review
/infra/**                    @hummbl-dev
*.tf                         @hummbl-dev
*.tfvars                     @hummbl-dev

# Policy and governance documents require governance team review
/policies/**                 @hummbl-dev
GOVERNANCE.md               @hummbl-dev
SECURITY.md                 @hummbl-dev

# GitHub Actions workflows require security review
/.github/workflows/**        @hummbl-dev

# Documentation changes
*.md                         @hummbl-dev
ARCHITECTURE.md             @hummbl-dev
